# 🌿 Cassava Leaf Disease Classification with CNN 🌿

This project implements a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) to classify cassava leaf diseases using transfer learning.  
The model is trained on the [Cassava Leaf Disease Classification dataset from Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/cassava-leaf-disease-classification/overview).

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🚀 Project Overview

Cassava is a major food crop in many tropical countries, but it is vulnerable to several diseases which reduce its yield and quality.  
Early and accurate detection of these diseases using machine learning can help farmers take timely action.

This project fine-tunes a pretrained CNN model to classify images of cassava leaves into different disease categories.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

