## ⚙️ Requirements

- Python 3.x  
- torch  
- torchvision  
- scikit-learn  
- pandas  
- matplotlib  
- Pillow  

Install dependencies with:

```bash
pip install torch torchvision scikit-learn pandas matplotlib pillow
